##############################
# passwd_exp input structure #
##############################

Fields in Input Order separated by `:'

	u_name			- user name
	u_fullname		- user full name
	u_email			- user email
	t_expire_date		- expire days
	t_disable_date		- date of dissable in days
	d_warn_days		- warning days
	d_inactive_days		- inactive days
	s_nosend		- user nosend bit
	*			- special user vars separator char


NOTE: One input structure per line is expected !